http://localhost:3000/api/calorie/goal (post) (setting calorie goal)
json: {
  "calorieGoal": 2200
}
http://localhost:3000/api/calorie/log (post) (adding a calorie log)
{
  "mealType": "lunch",
  "calories": 700
}
output of this :
{
  "_id": "685fb94740493085eb25e981",   <-- This is the document ID of the entire calorie log
  "user": "685971ed5fd982c78f27a01d",  <-- This is the ID of the user (from Users collection)
  ...
  "meals": [
    {
      "mealType": "lunch",
      "calories": 700,
      "confirmed": false,
      "_id": "685fb97140493085eb25e984"  <-- This is the ID of the individual meal subdocument
    }
  ],
  ...
}
http://localhost:3000/api/calorie/today (get) (getting today's calorie log)
output of this :
{
    "_id": "685fb94740493085eb25e981", <-- This is the document ID of the entire calorie log
    "user": "685971ed5fd982c78f27a01d",<-- This is the ID of the user (from Users collection)
    "date": "2025-06-28",
    "totalCalories": 700,
    "meals": [
        {
            "mealType": "lunch",
            "calories": 700,
            "confirmed": false,
            "_id": "685fb97140493085eb25e984"<-- This is the ID of the individual meal subdocument
        }
    ],
    "calorieGoal": 2200,
    "__v": 1
}
 Confirm a Meal (When User Clicks Notification)
 http://localhost:3000/api/calorie/confirm (patch)
 Output of this :
 {
    "message": "Meal confirmed",
    "log": {
        "_id": "685fb94740493085eb25e981",<-- This is the document ID of the entire calorie log
